Package: mgcv.helper
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions for mgcv
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Sam Clifford
Maintainer: Sam Clifford <samuel.clifford@qut.edu.au>
Description:
    This package provides a method for obtaining confidence intervals from a 
    fitted gam object from mgcv the way we would expect an lm or nls object to,
    and a way to calculate variance inflation factors for gam objects.  
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
